                            <div class="inner-single-blog title-single-blog anim-elem">
                                <h1>Must-Visit in 2018 International Cosmetic Shows</h1>
                            </div>
                            <div class="inner-single-blog image-single-blog anim-elem">
                                <img src="/upload/images/1512323870.jpg" alt="Must-Visit in 2018 International Cosmetic Shows">
                                <div class="inner-image-one-post-ss"></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="inner-single-blog desc-single-blog anim-elem">
                            <p><strong><a href="http://cosmobeautybarcelona.com/en/" target="_blank">COSMOBEAUTY</a> (Barcelona, Spain, 20−22 January) </strong>in 2017 was the meeting point of the most prominent brands and the best professionals of the sector: more than 50&thinsp;000 visitors, more than 1&thinsp;100 brands, 350 exhibitors and more than 10&thinsp;000 m2 of exhibition area.
 </p>
<p><strong><a href="https://www.vivaness.de/en" target="_blank">VIVANESS</a> (Nuremberg, Germany, 14&nbsp;&mdash; 17 February 2018) </strong>the trade fair for natural and organic cosmetics, was attended in 2017 by 258 exhibitors and 51&thinsp;453 trade visitors from 129 countries </p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.ibsnewyork.com" target="_blank">International Beauty Show</a> (New York, USA, 4−6 March) </strong>is the longest-running professionals-only event in beauty industry attended by 65&thinsp;200 serious beauty pros and 500 top exhibitors</p>
<p><strong><a href="https://www.beauty-duesseldorf.com" target="_blank">BEAUTY</a> (Dusseldorf, Germany, 9−11 March)</strong> is leading International Trade Fair Cosmetics, Nail, Foot, Wellness, Spa, in excess of 55&thinsp;000 visitors in 2017 and presentation of 1&thinsp;500 exhibitors and brands confirmed its top position as the sector&rsquo;s No. 1 trade fair.</p>
<p><strong><a href="https://www.top-hair-international.com" target="_blank">Top Hair International</a> (Dusseldorf, Germany, 10−11 March)</strong> is the world&rsquo;s No. 1 trade fair for the international hairdressing industry. The fair takes place once a year in Dusseldorf and is open to trade visitors only. 
 </p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.cosmoprof.com" target="_blank">Cosmoprof</a> (Bologna, Italy, 15−19 March)</strong> assembles more than 2300 exhibiting organizations from 58 countries and around 250&thinsp;000 visitors from 150 countries, who wish to promote their beauty and cosmetics products in the international market and conduct sales extensively.
 </p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.in-cosmetics.com/about-the-show/" target="_blank">in-cosmetics</a> (Amsterdam, Netherlands, 17−19 April)</strong> is the leading event for personal care ingredients. The most recent show attracted 8&thinsp;791 unique visitors and 780 exhibitors
 </p>
<p><strong><a href="http://en.cosmofarma.com" target="_blank">Cosmofarma</a> (Bologna, Italy, 20−22 April) </strong>is the pharmacy world&rsquo;s leading European event for the Health Care and Beauty Care sectors and all pharmacy-related services. More than 512 exhibitors will be participating at Cosmofarma and each of them will display the best range of medical products. 
 </p>
<p><a href="https://www.americasbeautyshow.com" target="_blank"><strong>America&rsquo;s Beauty Show</strong></a><strong> (Chicago, USA, 28−30 April) </strong>is biggest beauty show with more than 4000 exhibitors and 80&thinsp;000+ visitors: salon professionals and owners, aspiring students and teachers, headliners and educators, leading product manufacturers and distributors <br></p>
<p><strong><a href="http://beautyworld-japan.jp.messefrankfurt.com/tokyo/en/exhibitors/welcome.html" target="_blank">Beautyworld</a> (Tokyo, Japan, 14−16 May)</strong> gathering over 620 exhibitors and over 73000 visitors, Beautyworld is the ideal platform for discovering exciting new products and spoting the latest trends in the beauty industry.
 </p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.cosmetic-business.com/tradefair/en/" target="_blank">CosmeticBusiness</a> (Munich, Germany, 6−7 June)</strong> is the one and only meeting place for the cosmetics industry and its suppliers in Germany, Europe&rsquo;s largest cosmetics market. </p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.chemspeceurope.com/2018/english/" target="_blank">Chemspec</a> Europe (Cologne, Germany, 20−21 June)</strong> is Europe&rsquo;s premier sourcing and networking event for the fine and speciality chemicals industry. The exhibition is the central marketplace for manufacturers, suppliers and distributors of fine and speciality chemicals. Chemspec Europe 2017 in Munich registered thoroughly positive results: 401 exhibitors from 29 countries and 6&thinsp;476 attendees from all over the world</p>
<p><strong><a href="https://www.cosmetica.de/en/" target="_blank">COSMETICA</a> (Frankfurt, Germany, 24−25 June)</strong> is expecting around 600 companies and brands on an area of 17500 m2 at COSMETICA Frankfurt. The diverse representation of nature cosmetics, nail art, permanent make-up, lashes, chiropody and accessoires creates a varied spectrum of beauty products. An exciting mixture of established and innovative nurturing, appliance and decorative cosmetics amplifies the spectrum even further.</p>
<p><a href="http://cosmoprofnorthamerica.com/exhibition/" target="_blank"><strong>Cosmoprof North America</strong></a><strong> (Las Vegas, USA, 29−31 July) </strong>furthered its reputation as the leading B2B beauty trade show by introducing revolutionary technologies and forward-thinking programs. Over 36&thinsp;000 attendees engaged with a record-breaking 1&thinsp;278 exhibitors from 45 countries</p>
<p><a href="http://professionalbeauty.co.uk/e/Ireland/site/Home" target="_blank"><strong>Professional Beauty</strong></a><strong> (Dublin, Ireland, 7−8 October) </strong>is Ireland&rsquo;s leading beauty, spa and hair show</p><p><strong><a href="http://beauty-forum.fr/exposer_presentation.aspx" target="_blank">BEAUTY FORUM</a> (Paris, France, 7−8 October) </strong>showcases products like Cosmetics, treatment apparatus, spa, perfumes, pedicure tools, nail design etc. </p>
<p><strong><a href="https://www.cosmetic-360.com/en/" target="_blank">Cosmetic 360</a> </strong><strong>(Paris, France, 17−18 October)</strong> is an international exhibition dedicated to innovations and solutions for the perfumery&cosmetics industry.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.beauty-fairs.com/trade-shows/" target="_blank">BEAUTY FORUM</a> (Munich, Germany, 27−28 October)</strong> will be held at the International Trade Fair Ground in Munich for the 33nd time. Every year it attract more than 40&thinsp;000 visitors to the exhibition of more than 1&thinsp;000 brands and companies.
 </p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.ifema.es/salonlook_06/" target="_blank">SALÓN LOOK</a> (Madrid, Spain, 5−7 November)</strong> is the key event for the beauty, image and integral aesthetics sector in Spain. In its last edition, the event saw the participation of 397 exhibitors and more than 1&thinsp;200 national and international brands. This unique event for the image and comprehensive aesthetics sector offered 14&thinsp;200 m2 of innovative offerings and surprises, receiving visits from 67&thinsp;357 national and international professionals from Brazil, the USA, Italy and Portugal, among others.
 </p>
<p>More information about some 2018 trade fairs: <a href="http://helicopter-view.com/blog/top-drink-beverage-trade-shows-around-the-world" target="_blank">Top Drink & Beverage Trade Shows around the World</a>, <a href="http://helicopter-view.com/blog/baselworld-cuts-number-of-exhibitors-by-half" target="_blank">BaselWorld Cuts Number of Exhibitors by Half</a>, <a href="http://helicopter-view.com/blog/top-international-footwear-trade-shows">Top International Footwear Trade Shows</a>, <a href="http://helicopter-view.com/blog/top-international-children-and-maternity-trade-shows" target="_blank">Top International Children and Maternity Trade Shows</a>, <a href="http://helicopter-view.com/blog/the-best-gem-and-jewelry-trade-shows" target="_blank">The Best Gem and Jewelry Trade Shows</a>, <a href="http://helicopter-view.com/blog/biggest-international-boat-yacht-shows" target="_blank">Biggest International Boat & Yacht Shows</a>, <a href="http://helicopter-view.com/blog/must-visit-in-2018-international-cosmetic-shows" target="_blank">Must-Visit in 2018 International Cosmetic Shows</a>, <a href="http://helicopter-view.com/blog/top-international-golf-trade-shows" target="_blank">Top International Golf Trade Shows</a></p>
<p>Read more about new consumers: <a href="http://helicopter-view.com/public/blog/retail-future">Retail Future</a>, <a href="http://helicopter-view.com/public/blog/top-10-lessons-for-retailers1">Top 10 Lessons for Retailers</a>, <a href="http://helicopter-view.com/public/blog/retail-and-consumer-products-trends">Retail and Consumer Products Trends</a>, How do consumers shop (<a href="http://helicopter-view.com/public/blog/how-do-consumers-shop-part1" target="_blank">Part 1</a>, <a href="http://helicopter-view.com/public/blog/how-do-consumers-shop-part2" target="_blank">Part 2</a>), <a href="http://helicopter-view.com/public/blog/urban-world-the-global-consumers-to-watch" target="_blank">Urban World: The Global Consumers to Watch</a><br></p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
